Package: jormungandR
Version: 0.98.0
Date: 2019-10-04
Title: Python for Bioconductor
Authors@R: c(person("Aaron", "Lun", role=c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
        email="infinite.monkeys.with.keyboards@gmail.com"))
Depends: reticulate
biocViews: Infrastructure
Description: 
    Installs a local version of Python.
    This aims to provide a consistent Python version that can be used reliably by Bioconductor packages.
    Any new modules are installed inside a directory owned by R and are isolated from the system Python installation.
License: GPL-3
SystemRequirements: libffi
